title: The Indie Shop
desc: Please join us for a great indie naqil polish event! There will be meet and greets, demos, raffles and so much more! Come support your local indie nail polish makers including Bliss Polish, Lavish Polish, Sealore Polish, Cinema Swatch Lacquer, Nail Redesigned, Bad Bitch Polish, My Dream Polish, Squishy Face Polish, Stached Polish, Poetry Cowgirl Nail Polish, Nvr Enuff Polish, Painted Polish & Envy Lacquer!
